snippet.title: [Solo Leveling:ARISE] Character Teaser #1: Sung Jinwoo
snippet.description:
Solo Leveling:ARISE   
🎬 Character Teaser: Sung Jin-Woo

The weakest hunter of all mankind, reawakened as a player and the The Monarch of Shadows.

ARISE! Witness Sung Jin-Woo in action in this breathtaking teaser! 

Check out in-game footage from the upcoming  Solo Leveling:ARISE   
The popular webtoon, reborn as an action RPG!

Want to learn more? Then keep a lookout for updates on our official channel:
